Name:           gap-rds
Version:        1.9
Release:        0
Summary:        GAP: A package for searching relative difference sets
License:        GPL-2.0-or-later
Group:          Productivity/Scientific/Math
URL:            https://gap-packages.github.io/rds/
#Git-Clone:     https://github.com/gap-packages/rds
